data.description: Inside this ranch home you'll find 4 bedrooms & 2 baths!!! Don't wait to schedule your showing! This home also features formal living room, large laundry room with tons of storage. A kitchen with storage for all your chefs tools. A large family room/dining space with a deck off the back into the fenced back yard for outdoor entertaining. A 24 x 24 shop and a storage shed. Home also has a two car attached carport.
